{"tid":1335833,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網民印遊行橫額取貨發現被寫侮辱字句    BannerSHOP致歉稱會徹查","createTime":"2019-07-20T16:29:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T04:09:12.000Z","uid":48093,"like":3,"dislike":74,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"69d7c8d64e3f620bd076e3d458c9c41823deb47f","tid":1335833,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T16:29:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190721/large/1563639747_f3f4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190721%2Flarge%2F1563639747_f3f4.jpg&h=7f825a34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n民陣將於今日（21日）舉行遊行，有參與者已準備道具上街，其中有人模仿警方的黑、紅警示旗，二次創作成上街道具。有網民在連登討論區上載一張相片，指朋友到BannerSHOP印製一幅模仿警方紅旗，改成「無人衝擊 停止濫用武力（NO One Is Charging Stop Using Excessive Force）」，收貨後正面印製如常，但背後空白處竟被手寫上「返屋企X老母啦 廢青」。<br />\n<br />\n帖文一出即惹來大批網民熱烈討論，有人建議樓主退貨，亦有人直指BannerSHOP「可恥」，要求店舖道歉，另有不少人呼籲向店舖投訴。<br />\n<br />\nBannerSHOP晚上在facebook發出聲明，指BannerSHOP一直致力幫助不同公司或大家發表意見，同時亦尊重每位的意見和想法或活動，就論壇帖文提及的事情及行為表示非常關注，公司將會進行及深入調查並採取行動，以確保和了解事情的真實狀況，並自稱「身為一間100%香港人公司，我們和大家一樣，我們愛香港，愛香港既（嘅）自由言論！」聲明指對於事件或向大家造成影響，深抱歉意，呼籲若有任何疑問或資訊可以協助調查事件，歡迎大家電郵或致電查詢。"},{"pid":"22501de2dcd32a07cdce0ee9b6c100c4c2fddb87","tid":1335833,"uid":220182,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T17:06:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />邊個寫呢句幫公司宣傳得咁犀利"},{"pid":"ab2e67866147bf0d69423d3090544ad9fa8cf3bd","tid":1335833,"uid":83602,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T17:09:00.000Z","msg":"比個機會佢交代清楚<br />\n唔係以後唔撚幫襯"},{"pid":"746850b9d3af31f866c0c5ba2f15c59ffb6fc11c","tid":1335833,"uid":29093,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T17:10:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">身為一間100%香港人公司</span><br />\n<br />\n仲講得出口,  有冇面紅 ?  <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c79109613a735039bcd200cf073081a04d1a39aa","tid":1335833,"uid":173849,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T17:10:58.000Z","msg":"葡國人都為港發聲，我感動到立即去肥媽facebook比like，721為阿媽再次上街<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1335842\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1335842</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8e2bfef66a376d76a9e2d82d955680340a2c3851","tid":1335833,"uid":108337,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T17:12:31.000Z","msg":"最緊要要佢交一個人頭出黎"},{"pid":"4d9e98ba8ab8dc7304f446cd8a70ce53d6086a61","tid":1335833,"uid":18194,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T17:14:18.000Z","msg":"我公司已blacklist呢間野"},{"pid":"aa31dbd5bbb86333682b43cd8c806d0056c0596b","tid":1335833,"uid":92448,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T17:14:42.000Z","msg":"點都要炒人啦下？"},{"pid":"c77a7ae1367eab60b365c07716748d73e36cfd39","tid":1335833,"uid":2429,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T17:15:46.000Z","msg":"又貴又唔好用。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70b3b29948ec83d85f5cd028cc55565a587b4592","tid":1335833,"uid":280153,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T17:16:26.000Z","msg":"區區小店學人搞政治審查<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n何德何能呀垃圾"},{"pid":"f975745b5cbb2166b93601494262bf5d67f8e5f4","tid":1335833,"uid":78769,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T17:19:34.000Z","msg":"其實返工唔洗咁主動宣揚自己政治立場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"135bf259184743d390d63e9f0d5895a58df36355","tid":1335833,"uid":37931,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"746850b9d3af31f866c0c5ba2f15c59ffb6fc11c","tid":1335833,"uid":29093,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T17:10:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">身為一間100%香港人公司</span